(128,	'<p>This is an application to help you understand more about God through biblical historical documents</p><p>Make yourself a good habit of reading a scripture and praying every night, which will help you improve your soul to live through bible verses.</p><p>In addition, the application also provides images to describe each corresponding biblical passage to help people more intuitively understand the plot. And lots of warm, inspiring voices to make this bible app special</p><p>You can also save book chapters to read when connected to the network, the corresponding photo and audio collection will be saved with that chapter.</p><p><strong>-Special features:</strong><br />+ Describe the image of the story<br />+ You can save bible books to read without a network connection<br />+ Demonstration function for you to choose to create beautiful background pictures of the bible or share it with friends via social network<br />+ Support many languages ​​in the world<br />+ Reading and listening to the document</p>'),
(121,	'<p>You are sad?<br />Are you lonely?<br />Have not you ever had a love affair?<br />Want to find a maid in your phone?<br />Or simply you want to find a friend to chat?<br /><br />This is an application that helps you solve those problems<br />You will have a cute girlfriend, lurking, lurking with you, always make fun of jokes. will follow you on the cold winter days, hot summer days<br /><br />Especially you can err, give orders to do simple tasks such as compose, call, play music, etc. .. have such a docile love everyone does not like it!<br /><br />Not only that, this virtual lover application also brings you many interesting features such as:<br /><br />+ Chat<br />-Chat<br />-Remember<br />- Sing to you<br />- Read the story<br />-Memory-language love<br />-Learn foreign language<br />- Guess the user emotion<br />- Describe the user\'s personality through questions<br />+ Virtual Assistant<br />Control the system with commands, user talk (eg open applications, messages, call etc.)<br />+ Virtual reality<br />- create virtual reality environment<br />- Create realistic virtual environments with realistic lifestyles</p>'),
(122,	'<p><strong>application, game help for those insomnia, sleeplessness. With 2 function &quot;Go to sleep&quot; and &quot;gaming&quot;.</strong></p><p>Counting sheep - go to bed is an arcade game where you&#39;ll find tons of sheep ready to help you fall asleep. In a relatively simple way, the app aims to help you to relax using songs and calm rhythms as you count all these animals and drift off into a deep slumber.</p><p>In Counting sheep - go to bed you&#39;ll also find two minigames that will test your skills. In one of them you&#39;ll have to tap on all the sheep that come close to an apple. With this you&#39;ll prevent the animals from getting the fruit while you rack up points on the scoreboard. In the second one, all you have to do is tap on the characters so that they can jump over a wooden obstacle.</p><p>Another great feature in Counting sheep - go to bed is that you can select the number of sheep you want to count. This way you can increase or decrease the number of animals that you have to look out for as you start drifting off to sleep. In addition, from the main menu you can also select the song you want to play during the counting process.</p><p>Counting sheep - go to bed has 3D graphics that make it easy to see all the sheep on the screen. With a long list of songs, you&#39;ll have everything you need to select the one you like best and try to fall asleep as soon as possible. You&#39;ll even have a scoreboard where you can see your score compared to that of other players.</p><p><br /><br /><strong>Special Features</strong><br />- Music hall to go to bed<br />- Read the good wishes of everyone in the world<br />- Player ratings in game mode<br />- 3d graphics</p>'),
